high_descs: Turn around and go to the bed.
Take the knife from the bed.
There is a potato on the bed.
Cut the potato into pieces using the knife.
Put the knife on the bed.
Take the potato from the bed.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave oven.
Then take it out and go to the sink.
Put the potato into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Potato into the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Walk towards and turn left to the bed.
Pick the knife from the bed.
Turn left to the bed.
Cut the potato on the bed.
Place the knife on the bed.
Pick a piece of potato from the bed.
Turn right and turn left and then turn right to the microwave.
Put the potato inside the microwave.
Pick it out of the microwave and turn right and walk towards the sink.
Place the potato inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the potato inside the sink.

high_descs: Move through the hall and turn left towards the bed in the bedroom.
Take the knife from the bed.
turn around and move towards the potato.
Cut the potato into slices.
Place the knife on the extreme right end of the bed.
Take the potato in the hand.
Turn left, head through the door and move right through hallway towards the microwave in the kitchen.
Open the oven, place the potato slice inside for some time and take the potato out and close the oven.
Turn around and move right towards the hallway to the sink in the toilet.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move the cooked Potato to the SinkBasin
